{"sn45.38:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 45.38 ","sn45.38:0.2":"4. Patipattivagga ","sn45.38:0.3":"Dutiyabrahmannasutta ","sn45.38:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn45.38:1.2":"“Brahmannanca vo, bhikkhave, desessami, brahmannatthanca. ","sn45.38:1.3":"Tam sunatha. ","sn45.38:1.4":"Katamanca, bhikkhave, brahmannam? ","sn45.38:1.5":"Ayameva ariyo atthangiko maggo, seyyathidam—","sn45.38:1.6":"sammaditthi …pe… sammasamadhi. ","sn45.38:1.7":"Idam vuccati, bhikkhave, brahmannam. ","sn45.38:1.8":"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, brahmannattho? ","sn45.38:1.9":"Yo kho, bhikkhave, ragakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—","sn45.38:1.10":"ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, brahmannattho”ti. ","sn45.38:1.11":"Atthamam. "}